---
title: General Tso's Tofu with Steamed Broccoli & Rice
description: Sometimes you want takeout flavors, but the joy of making the dish all yourself. We hear you! Why not show off those takeout-cooking chops every once in a while? Our chefs bring you all the General Tso’s flavors you already love, right to your kitchen counter. You’ll start by cooking fluffy rice and steaming broccoli in the microwave. Then, you’ll coat tofu in tempura batter and fry it all up. Drizzle everything in a sesame soy sauce with ginger and garlic, serve it over a bed of rice, and you’ve got yourself the familiar veg-ified dish that’s Tso Tso tasty.
